---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for RG Extreme Pressure — how we collect, use, and protect your personal data.">
  <section class="policy">
    <div class="policy__inner">
      <h1 class="policy__heading">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="policy__updated">Last updated: June 2025</p>

      <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
      <p>RG Extreme Pressure ("we", "us", "our") is a sole trader based in Bath, Somerset. Our website is <strong>rgextremepressure.co.uk</strong>. For any privacy queries, contact us at <a href="mailto:galazkarobert@yahoo.co.uk">galazkarobert@yahoo.co.uk</a> or call <a href="tel:+447474939398">07474 939 398</a>.</p>

      <h2>2. What Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you use our website or contact us, we may collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Contact information</strong> — name, email address, phone number, and postal address when you submit our contact form or email us directly.</li>
        <li><strong>Project details</strong> — information about your property and project requirements that you share with us.</li>
        <li><strong>Technical data</strong> — IP address, browser type, device type, and pages visited, collected automatically via cookies and analytics.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <p>We use your personal data to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Respond to enquiries and provide quotations</li>
        <li>Deliver the building and maintenance services you've requested</li>
        <li>Communicate about project progress and scheduling</li>
        <li>Improve our website and services</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
      <p>We process your data under the following GDPR Article 6 bases:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Contract</strong> — to provide quotations and deliver services you've requested</li>
        <li><strong>Consent</strong> — when you submit our contact form or subscribe to communications</li>
        <li><strong>Legitimate interest</strong> — to improve our services and website functionality</li>
        <li><strong>Legal obligation</strong> — to comply with UK law and regulations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Cookies and Analytics</h2>
      <p>Our website uses cookies for essential functionality. We may use analytics tools to understand how visitors use the site. You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>

      <h2>6. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell or rent your personal data. We may share data with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Service providers</strong> — hosting, email, and analytics platforms that process data on our behalf</li>
        <li><strong>Legal authorities</strong> — when required by law or to protect our rights</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain your personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes for which it was collected, including legal, accounting, or reporting requirements. Enquiry data is retained for 12 months unless a business relationship is established.</p>

      <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Under UK GDPR and the Data Protection Act 2018, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Rectify inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request erasure of your data</li>
        <li>Restrict processing</li>
        <li>Data portability</li>
        <li>Object to processing</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:galazkarobert@yahoo.co.uk">galazkarobert@yahoo.co.uk</a>.</p>

      <h2>9. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect your personal data against unauthorised access, loss, or destruction. Our website is served over HTTPS to encrypt data in transit.</p>

      <h2>10. International Transfers</h2>
      <p>Your data is stored and processed within the UK and EEA. Where third-party services process data outside these regions, we ensure adequate safeguards are in place.</p>

      <h2>11. Complaints</h2>
      <p>If you believe your data has been mishandled, you have the right to lodge a complaint with the Information Commissioner's Office (ICO) at <a href="https://ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ico.org.uk</a>.</p>

      <h2>12. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The updated version will be published on this page with a revised "Last updated" date.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .policy {
    background: #fff;
    padding: var(--section-pad) var(--gutter);
  }

  .policy__inner {
    max-width: 72ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .policy__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 0 0 0.25em;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .policy__updated {
    color: var(--concrete);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .policy__inner h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 2rem 0 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .policy__inner p {
    color: var(--concrete);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .policy__inner ul {
    color: var(--concrete);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5em;
  }

  .policy__inner li {
    margin-bottom: 0.35em;
  }

  .policy__inner a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .policy__inner a:hover {
    color: var(--navy);
  }
</style>